title: Google Earth Engine Proxy for openEO
description:
This is the Google Earth Engine Driver for openEO.

Google Earth Engine is a planetary-scale platform for Earth science data & analysis. It is powered by Google's cloud infrastructure and combines a multi-petabyte catalog of satellite imagery and geospatial datasets with planetary-scale analysis capabilities. Google makes it available for scientists, researchers, and developers to detect changes, map trends, and quantify differences on the Earth's surface. Google Earth Engine is free for research, education, and nonprofit use.
